ed="T" n="0800c22"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0800c22"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000009882"><placeName>蘇州</placeName><placeName>開元寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A010899">辯秀</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0800c23"/><persName key="A010899">釋辯秀</persName>，俗姓<name>劉</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000000097">漢</placeName><persName key="A011006"><persName>楚王</persName><persName>交</persName></persName>三十一代孫也。<lb
ed="T" n="0800c24"/><persName key="A010899">秀</persName>幼孤，諸父哀字<ptr type="glossary" target="#g533"/>，禮如教立，孝自天生<ptr target="#n453"/>。而<lb
ed="T" n="0800c25"/><anchor xml:id="beg0800sgsz5"/>宿植<anchor xml:id="end0800sgsz5"/>緣深，心田欲稔；因請伯氏<ptr target="#n1265"/>，出家長行<ptr type="glossary" target="#g534"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0800c26"/>哀而捨旃<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1050"/>。事<placeName key="PL000000011596">靈隱</placeName><ref type="person" target="#A010894"><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>謀</sic><corr>某</corr></choice>禪師</ref><ptr target="#n1266"/>，便能問津，圖入<lb
ed="T" n="0800c27"/>道之意。所聞指訓，如涼風入懷，醒然清悟。<lb
ed="T" n="0800c28"/><date from-iso="+0745-02-10" key="j19932061993559" to-iso="+0746-01-29"><name>天寶</name>四年</date>，受戒於<placeName key="PL000000010411">東海</placeName><persName key="A010883">鑒真<ptr target="#n454"/><roleName>大師</roleName></persName>，傳律於<placeName key="PL000000013239">會<lb
ed="T" n="0800c29"/>稽</placeName><persName key="A004177">曇一</persName>。<date notBefore-iso="+0756-08-16" key="j19974111997993" notAfter-iso="+0758-03-21"><name>至德</name>中</date>舉高行，隷名於<placeName key="PL000000009882"><placeName>吳郡</placeName><placeName>開元<pb ed="T" n="0801a" xml:id="T50.2061.0801a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0801a01"/>寺</placeName></placeName>。<date notBefore-iso="+0758-03-22" key="j19979941998806" notAfter-iso="+0760-06-11"><name>乾元</name>中</date>，下詔天下二十五寺，各定大德<lb
ed="T" n="0801a02"/>七人，長講戒律，<persName key="A010899">秀</persName>應其數也。頃年於淨土<lb
ed="T" n="0801a03"/>一門，不愆于念。嘗謂人曰：「昔聞西方之行<lb
ed="T" n="0801a04"/>是有相大乘<ptr target="#n1271"/>，此乃蓬心<ptr type="glossary" target="#g535"/>不直，非達觀之說<ptr target="#n1267"/>。何<lb
ed="T" n="0801a05"/>邪？夫出言即性，發意皆如，而一色一香，無非<lb
ed="T" n="0801a06"/>中道<ptr type="glossary" target="#g537"/>，況<ptr target="#n1268"/>我正念<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1133"/>乎？」<persName key="A010899">秀</persName>壇場一十六番，度人<placeName key="PL000000048398">孤</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0801a07"/>制，律樞正持，僧<anchor xml:id="beg0801001"/>綱<anchor xml:id="end0801001"/>自<anchor xml:id="beg0801002"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>肯</sic><corr>胥</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0801002"/><ptr type="glossary" target="#g72"/>，<placeName key="PL000000008559">湖</placeName>南、北皆宗仰焉<ptr target="#n458"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0801a08"/>以<date key="j20061552006155" when-iso="+0780-07-25"><name>建中</name>元年六月十五日</date>寢疾而終，春秋六<lb
ed="T" n="0801a09"/>十七，法臘三十五<ptr target="#n1269"/>。當其逝日，有庭樹一本，<lb
ed="T" n="0801a10"/>枝葉扶疎，朝<anchor xml:id="beg0801sgsz1"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0801sgsz1"/>正敷<ptr target="#n1270"/>而遽萎瘁。<date key="j20061742006174" when-iso="+0780-08-13">其年七月五<lb
ed="T" n="0801a11"/>日</date>，遷靈龕於<placeName key="PL000000010019">武丘西寺</placeName>松門之右。門人<persName key="A011007">道亮</persName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0801a12"/><persName key="A011008">道該</persName>、<persName key="A011009">清會</persName>，偕遶<anchor xml:id="beg0801sgsz2"/>旃檀<anchor xml:id="end0801sgsz2"/>之香樹也<ptr target="#n1317"/>。故觀察使<persName key="A011010">韋<lb
ed="T" n="0801a13"/>元甫</persName>、<persName key="A011011">李棲筠</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000025169">虢州</placeName>刺史<persName key="A010957">李紓</persName>、御史中丞<persName key="A011012">李道<lb
ed="T" n="0801a14"/>昌</persName>盡欽慕往德，亦林下之交。<placeName key="PL000000013012">霅</placeName><persName key="A008833">晝</persName>為碑頌<lb
ed="T" n="0801a15"/>焉。</p>
